    <text type="letter">
        <body>
            <pb xml:id="leaf001r" facs="loc.01379.002_large.jpg" type="recto"/>
            <opener>
                <dateline>
                    <name type="place">Camden, NJ America</name>
                    <date when="1888-09-02"><hi rend="underline">Sunday</hi> Evng Sept: 2 '88<ptr target="loc.07521_n1"/></date>
                </dateline>
            </opener>
            <p>Your good letter just rec'd<ptr target="loc.07521_n2"/>  &#38; here I am sending word back&#8212;still imprisoned in
                my sick room&#8212;non-rehabilitated yet but middling well for all that&#8212;my
                booklet <hi rend="underline">November Boughs</hi><ptr target="n3999"/> ab't finish'd&#8212;&#38; a large vol.
                comprising all my stuff begun<ptr target="n4151"/>&#8212;I am here just at sunset&#8212;Love to you all
                old &#38; young&#8212;I sufficiently comfortable</p>
            <closer>
                <signed>Walt Whitman</signed>
            </closer>
            <pb xml:id="leaf001v" facs="loc.01379.001_large.jpg" type="verso"/>
        </body>
